Class ReferenceCountingBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.ReferenceCountingBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReferenceCounting
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicTrainable, ComponentTestBase, CudaResourceBase, CudaTensor, DoubleBuffer, DoubleBufferSet, ImgLinearSubnetLayer.SubnetLeg, InnerNode, IterativeTrainer, LineSearchCursorBase, LineSearchPoint, OrientationStrategyBase, PointSample, RegisteredObjectBase, ReshapedTensorList, Result, SimpleEval, SimpleListEval, Tensor, TensorListTrainable, TrainableBase, TrainableWrapper

    public abstract class ReferenceCountingBase
extends Object
implements ReferenceCounting
    The base implementation for ReferenceCounting objects. Provides state management and debugging facilities. If assertions are enabled, stack traces are recorded to provide detailed logs for debugging LifecycleExceptions.
